@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kzsmvr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.46) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.31)) * (0.77 / (v0 + 0.33 * v2 + 0.56)))
    tmp = v1
    v0 = ((0.76 - (v2 + 0.04 + tmp + 0.33)) * (wp.sin(v2 + 0.62) * (v0 + 0.16 * v0 + 0.78)))
    v1 = wp.cos(0.42)
    data[tid] = v0
